{"word":"G4026 - περιΐστημι - periḯstēmi - per-ee-is'-tay-mee - Avoid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιΐστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">periḯstēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-is'-tay-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Avoid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சூழ், விலகியிரு, விலகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to place around (one)"},{"paragraph":"2. to stand around"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a>; to <i>stand</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, (near) to <i>be a bystander</i>, or (aloof) to <i>keep away</i> from: - avoid, shun, stand by (round about).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}